h4. Description:
This is landing page of "Budget Line Item" Report with search panel on top.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks  [Budget|guide:renderBudgetMenu] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Budget Line Item" link.
* Show Landing Page of "Budget Line Item" Report.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Show search panel on top.
* Show project list in drop-down. [Populate Project List|application]

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show landing page of Inventory Item Reconciliation Report.
** Reset input form on top to search new report.
** Show grid view at the bottom of landing page.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

